            Undergraduate studies
          
An undergraduate education in ECE is the gateway to an incredibly promising career. Learn about our programs in computer engineering, electrical engineering, and engineering physics.






            Graduate studies
          
Earn a master's or doctoral degree in the heart of Chicago, a center for scholarship and industry.






            Faculty
          
Meet our full-time faculty members who represent the best in theory and practice.






            Research labs
          
Learn about the hubs of collaboration and innovation that drive UIC ECE.


















 

























